{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c8d36b3e94","title":"在中央政治局会议上对教育工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9a012f966f","index":0,"year":1963,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c8d36b3e94"}],"tags":[{"id":"299424f798","name":"教育和教育革命","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76ebe10bf9","type":"title","text":"在中央政治局会议上对教育工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c8d36b3e94"},{"id":"ea4f48a783","type":"paragraph","text":"学生健康不好的原因是伙食不好，卫生不好，功课重，课外负担过重，太忙。要增进学生健康，要增进营养，要克服忙的现象。要一面增加收入，一面减少消耗。因此要多增加助学金，改善伙食，另一面要克服忙乱现象。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c8d36b3e94"}],"page":{"id":"840cb22941","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c8d36b3e94","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}